core.​ XPS_typ_Enumeration

TypeDefinition

Authors

Crashdome

Description

Abstract Class. Derived classes created with XPS_fnc_createEnumeration will store a type-safe set of enumerations in the Values property which are constants (compileFinal'd).

This class is not meant to be inherited directly.  Use XPS_fnc_createEnumeration to generate them safely.

Parent

none

Implements

None
